The Bearing Compass tells you which direction
you are facing.

This can help you set the bounds of your ship and
figure out which direction you want to teleport in.

To use it, hold the Bearing Compass in your hand
and right click.  It should tell you in the chat:

Yaw
  Minecraft system - degrees clockwise from south
Bearing
  Orienteering system - degrees clockwise from north
Pitch
  Minecraft system - degrees down from horizontal
Inclination
  Orienteering system - degrees up from horizontal
Facing
  Axis direction closest to the way you are facing
Axis
  Axis corresponding to your facing direction